729565f-b.title: Richmond: Westervelt Avenue - Scribner Avenue
729565f-b.text:
St. George, Staten Island: Looking eastward across the
lower part of St. George and the Upper New York Bay as seen
from 389 Westervelt Avenue, at the head of Scribner Avenus..
The clock tower is that of Public School No. 16 on Daniel Low
Terrace. On the extreme right are riers and warehouses of the
American Dock Conpany and across the bay is the skyline of
Kings County (Brooklyn). View 3 is in a moe southerly direction
and shows the north slope of Tavilion Hill.
About November 1, 1926
Views 1, 2, 3
P. L. Sparr
NO .EPRODUCTIONS
